data.description: New HVAC in 2021. Back on the market due to buyers change of assignment.  Do I have the place for you!  Come settle in to this beautiful home situated in the highly desirable Sycamore Park Subdivision.  This turnkey 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is ready for you!  Inside you will find a large comfortable living space, kitchen with updated stainless steel appliances and room for your dining needs.  Step outside to enjoy your fully landscaped backyard on a corner lot with plenty of privacy.  Call to schedule your showing today!
